  "name": "Zephyr Strike",
  "type": "spell",
  "system": {
    "description": {
      "value": "<div class=\"rd__b  rd__b--3\"><p>You move like the wind. Until the spell ends, your movement doesn't provoke opportunity attacks.</p><div class=\"rd__spc-inline-post\"></div><p>Once before the spell ends, you can give yourself advantage on one weapon attack roll on your turn. That attack deals an extra [[/r 1d8]] force damage on a hit. Whether you hit or miss, your walking speed increases by 30 feet until the end of that turn.</p></div>",
